minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual;mso-no-proof:yes;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">1.1 总量：总人口连续13年下降，自然增长率降幅连续16年扩大</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">1.2 结构：儿童青少年占比全球倒二，老龄化程度世界第二</span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0.48px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;">1.3 迁移：东京都成为唯一人口正增长的都道府县，东京都市圈人口单极化逆势增长</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);letter-spacing: 0.034em;line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微