ox-sizing: border-box;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 2, 103);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">导读</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">杭州全面放开二手房限购！</span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">国家已经定调因城施策，一二线城市不用担心放松限购就会报复性反弹，时代一去不返了，广州、苏州等放松限购后市场并未明显复苏就是明证。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">逻辑变了，预期变了。</span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">如果房地产硬着陆，受伤最大的一定是普通老百姓，烂尾，家庭资大幅缩水，即使没有房子的人也会面临失业压力。房地产是周期之母，一定要高度重视，软着陆。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">很多发达经济体在城镇化尾声，房地产依旧是国民经济支柱行业。房地产是中国第一大支柱行业，关联60多个相关产业，几千万就业，<strong>要全面看待房地产对经济增长、土地财政的重要作用，不可“妖魔化”房地产</strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"><strong>。</strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">综合考虑城镇化进程、改善性需求、城市更新等，中国房地产市场未来需求下降，但中长期仍有发展空间。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;">近期万科流动性问题被市场高度关注。作为曾经的行业学习标杆，稳健经营的优秀榜样，如果连房企最后的堡垒都扛不住，说明唯一的办法是重启市场。<strong>在发展中解决问题，<strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">坚</strong></strong><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">持“房住不炒”，支持居民刚性住房需求和多样化改善性住房需求。</strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;">全面取消限购</span><span style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;">，持续大幅降息，组建万亿住房保障银行收购开发商库存，这三大组合拳缺一不可。</span></strong><span style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-indent: 2em;"></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;"></span></strong></span></p><div style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 530.475px;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow: hidden !important;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 303.3 4.6" style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" width="100%"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><path style="box-sizing: border-box;" d="M189.5,1.8c-1.4,0-2.7,0-4.1-0.3c-0.6-0.1-1.2-0.2-1.7-0.5c-0.3-0.1-1.5-1.3-1.3-0.4      c-0.4-0.4-1.2-1.2-1-0.1c0.1,0.4,0.6,1,0.6,1.4c0,0.1,0,0.3,0,0.4c0,0.1,0,0.2,0,0.4c0,0.4-0.5,1-0.6,1.3      c-0.2,1.1,0.6,0.3,1-0.2c-0.1,0.9,1.1-0.2,1.3-0.4c0.5-0.2,1.2-0.4,1.7-0.5c1.3-0.3,2.7-0.3,4.1-0.3c2.8,0,5.5-0.1,8.3-0.1      c1.8,0,97.5-0.1,99.1,0.4c0.6,0.2,1.7,0.8,2.4,0.5c0.9-0.4-0.5-0.9-0.8-1.3c0.2-0.4,1.7-0.9,0.8-1.3c-0.6-0.3-1.8,0.3-2.4,0.5      c-1.7,0.5-97.3,0.4-99.1,0.4C195,1.9,192.3,1.8,189.5,1.8z" fill="rgb(0,2,103)"></path></g><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><path style="box-sizing